snippet.textDisplay:
one thing people should know .. Rohail Hayat had ONLY 2 successful seasons out of 6! the first 2 season majority audience didnt notice... it was only that his experiment on Alif Allah song by Arif Lohar and Meesha Shafi got the 3rd season the recognition and applause from the audience! That song became viral along with a few more regional language tracks.. 
Audience got super excited for the 4th season! That season along with the 5th maintained the collaboration, groovy styled theme on local/regional songs and introducing new artists... some of them got appreciation, some liked the new singers.. so the 4th season was good but 5th season seemed boring and repetitive for the audience.. Then comes the decline of Rohail Hayat in the face of his 6th season .. Trying too hard to bring back the magic and that was the most flop season of all.. Strings had a huge responsibility since season 7 .. they tried themselves, they are trying by letting artists to produce songs.. 
And it seems like a smooth sail with a few blunders.. but who hasnt made those blunders! 
So please appreciate this song, appreciate the hard work these people are putting into all their songs!
Stop whining about the past
